{% doc %}
  @prompt
    New Message
    Create a 3-column comparison chart section for Shopify with the following structure:
    
    Section Title at the top: editable.
    
    Three Columns Layout:
    
    Left Column: Product image (editable), product title (editable), and a vertical list of checkmarks or crosses (✅ ❌). Each row should be editable in the customizer. Add horizontal divider lines between rows.
    
    Middle Column: A box with only one heading: 'Pound For Pound, Which Has More:' (editable text). No checkmarks or crosses here.
    
    Right Column: Product image (editable), product title (editable), and a vertical list of checkmarks or crosses (✅ ❌), matching the same number of rows as the left column. Also include horizontal divider lines.
    
    Style:
    
    Clean, mobile-responsive design.
    
    Middle column background: dark purple (#3b0a45), white text, rounded corners.
    
    Section heading color: pink (#d12c85).
    
    Divider lines: light gray.
    
    Center everything neatly aligned.
    
    The final design should look like a comparison chart, with ✅ ❌ in the left and right columns, and only a heading in the middle column.", show heading title in center column, want to set feature title in middle column only
    , make in mobile view like desktop view same layout, Left product Yes Replace with the background color pink & border rounded &  ❌ No it sholud be #2f0147 background color, Default settings:
       - Use ✔ checkmark in pink (#ff69b4)
       - Use ✘ cross in blue (#0052cc)
       - VS panel background in dark purple (#3d0052) with white text.
       - Rounded corners and subtle box shadows for cards., Feature 1 sholud be 13 sets

